t"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-b6U","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":19124,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/12\/five-pillars-and-family-ties\/","url_meta":{"origin":42712,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Perform the five pillars, be kind to family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ayyub reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cTell me what I can do to enter Paradise and avoid Hellfire.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWorship Allah and do not associate anything with Him, perform the prayer, give in charity, and keep\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7633,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/04\/husband-wife-rights-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":42712,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Rights: If a husband fails to fulfill his family&#8217;s rights","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Hind bint 'Utba came and she said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, Abu Sufyan is a stingy man. Is there any blame on me for using his wealth to feed our dependents?\" The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no blame if you feed them\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/07\/01\/prophet-does-chores\/","url_meta":{"origin":42712,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Chores: The Prophet does chores for his family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 1, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Aswad reported: I asked Aisha,\u00a0\u201cWhat did the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, do in his house?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cThe Prophet would do chores for his family and\u00a0he would go out\u00a0when it was time for prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 676 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0648\u064e\u062f\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0633\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0644\u0652\u062a\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34923,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/12\/iman-silat-al-rahim\/","url_meta":{"origin":42712,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Let him maintain his family relations","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 12, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever believes in Allah and the Last Day, let him uphold his family ties.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6138 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\